{{#extend "project" }}
{{#content "title" mode="append"}} - Redspread{{/content}}
{{#content "body-class" mode="append"}} page-redspread{{/content}}
{{#content "backgrounds" mode="append"}}
<li class="background-redspread-hero"></li>
<li class="background-redspread-brand"></li>
<li class="background-redspread-product"></li>
<li class="background-redspread-web"></li>
{{/content}}
{{#content "sections" mode="prepend"}}
<li class="animated-section project-hero section-redspread-hero" data-section-id="redspread-hero">
    <div class="content">
        <h1 class="project-title sc-text">Redspread</h1>
        <div class="project-img-wrapper">
            <img src="/img/redspread/redspread-macbook.png" alt="Redspread">
            <ul class="services">
                <li class="sc-text">Product Naming</li>
                <li class="sc-text">Brand Identity</li>
                <li class="sc-text">UI/UX Design</li>
                <li class="sc-text">Web Development</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <p class="project-summary sc-text">We built a brand, website, blog, and product with the Redspread team who make deployment tools and have since been acquired by CoreOS.</p>
        <div class="blockquote-wrapper">
            <blockquote class="sbd-accent sc-text">
                <div class="quote-upper-line sbg-accent"></div>
                <div class="quote-mark sf-svg-accent">{{> "icons/quote.svg"}}</div>
                <div class="quote-lower-line sbg-accent"></div>
                Minimill designed and developed a polished new website for us. As we started expanding our beta we were hoping to kick it up a notch. We accomplished that.
                <cite>
                    <span class="name sc-text">Mackenzie Burnett</span>
                    <span class="title sc-text">CEO, Redspread</span>
                    <span class="photo"><img src="/img/redspread/head-mackenzie.png" alt="Mackenzie Burnett"></span>
                </cite>
            </blockquote>
        </div>
    </div>
</li>
<li class="animated-section project-section section-redspread-brand" data-section-id="redspread-brand">
    <div class="content">
        <h2 class="h1 sc-text">Complex concepts in a friendly identity</h2>
        <div class="col-8 col-centered">
            <p class="large sc-text">The company formerly known as Distributed Systems approached us about a rebrand that would make their deployment tools more approachable on all user-facing surfaces. We came up with Redspread: an original identity that included name, logo, colors, and typography. The brand represents their all-encompasing approach to development, yet is flexible enough to support an evolving product landscape while maintaining core values of simplicity and openness.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="col-8 col-centered">
            <img class="project-screenshot padded" src="/img/redspread/redspread-logotype.svg" alt="Unscan Logotype">
        </div>
    </div>
