    <div class="content color-blocks">
        <div class="col-12">
            {{> color-block
            name="Red"
            hex="FF351A"
            class="dark"}}
            {{> color-block
            name="Blue"
            hex="0D7280"
            class="dark"}}
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
            {{> color-block
            name="Light Red"
            hex="FFF6F5"
            class="light"}}
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
            {{> color-block
            name="Light Blue"
            hex="F0F9FA"
            class="light"}}
        </div>
        <div class="col-12">
            {{> color-block
            name="Light Gray"
            hex="F9F9F9"
            class="light"}}
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content font-stacks">
        <div class="col-12">
            {{#embed "font-stack"
                name="Din Round"
                weight="Medium"
                class="has-15px-descenders" }}
                {{#content "svg"}}
                    {{> "typography/text-redspread-dinround.svg" }}
                {{/content}}
            {{/embed}}
            {{#embed "font-stack"
                name="Source Sans Pro"
                weight="Medium"
                class="has-10px-descenders" }}
                {{#content "svg"}}
                    {{> "typography/text-redspread-sourcesanspro.svg" }}
                {{/content}}
            {{/embed}}
        </div>
    </div>
</li>
<li class="animated-section project-section section-redspread-product" data-section-id="redspread-product">
    <div class="content">
        <h2 class="h1 sc-text">End-to-end product development</h2>
        <div class="col-8 col-centered">
            <p class="large sc-text">Redspread brought our team into their product development workflow from the beginning. Together, we designed and implemented their entire application. We created user interface patterns that we extended across multiple pages, making a complex application feel simple.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="col-12">
            <img class="project-screenshot" src="/img/redspread/redspread-monitor.png" alt="The Redspread app">
        </div>
    </div>
</li>
<li class="animated-section project-section section-redspread-web" data-section-id="redspread-web">
    <div class="content">
        <h2 class="h1 sc-text">Making deployment accessible to all audiences</h2>
        <div class="col-8 col-centered">
            <p class="large sc-text">Creating a landing page for Redspread presented a unique challenge: making a back-end product appealing to developers and executives alike. We combined UI snippets from the Redspread app with a screen recording of the spread command line tool to convey Redspread's feature set.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="col-12">
            <img class="project-screenshot" src="/img/redspread/redspread-web.png" alt="The Redspread marketing page and blog">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="col-8 col-centered">
            {{#embed "external-link"
            href="https://www.redspread.com/"
            iconClass="link"}}
            {{#content "icon"}}{{> "icons/link.svg" }}{{/content}}
            {{#content "h2"}}redspread.com{{/content}}
            {{/embed}}
        </div>
    </div>
</li>
{{> "footer" class="solid" id="redspread-footer" }}
{{/content}}
{{/extend}}
